<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Outline propertyt</title>
    <style>
        .chair{
            border: 2px solid black;
            padding: 34px;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px 5px rgb(12, 140, 226);
            background-color: rgb(19, 230, 205);

        }
        .text-element{ text-shadow: rgba(39, 10, 255, 0.756)
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="chair">
        I am a Chair.
       
    </div>
    
     <p class="text-element">Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Numquam, tempore consequuntur.
             Quaerat dolor repudiandae natus fugiat perspiciatis hic vel vero dolore voluptates temporibus?
    </p>

    
</body>
</html>